<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Dismantle" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Dismantle,</orth> to strip; properly and figuratively: <cit><quote>muffle your face, d. you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.666" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 666</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>this realm --d was of Jove himself,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.293" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 293</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to d. so many folds of favour,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 1.1.220" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 1, 220</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>